Jet is a JavaScript REST Server running on Mozilla SpiderMonkey with XPCOM/XPConnect functionality.

Based on the XULRunner stack, it supports extensions as per ordinary XULRunner/Firefox apps.

Download and copy the XULRunner binaries into Jet/bin directory.
See: ftp://ftp.mozilla.org/pub/mozilla.org/xulrunner/releases/

To run execute ./Jet




To create a symbolic link from jet/bin to xulrunner/bin 
ln -s /path/to/xulrunner/bin bin